::Cygnar::
    He flew up to the top of the newly opened Trainer base.  He spots Cyanide 
dropping in and follows him into the hole.  He looks to Cyanide.  "I don't 
think you should be here.  I have every intention of capturing this base 
myself.  Another person would just confuse him."  He nods at Ignatius.
